{"cursor":"19247","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"\n\n\n'Holiness', or 'sanctity', is in general the state of being 'holy' (perceived by\nreligious individuals as associated with the divine) [http://books.google.c-\nom/books?id=CDIGVRkxfDEC&pg=PT32&lpg=PT32&dq=perceived+by+religious+individuals-\n+as+associated+with+the+divine&source=bl&ots=qGoeSVtEy7&sig=qRI9W7dHb0i9Ydwu4qG-\n88is7kmo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=PTA6UMCYM4ik8ATPk4DoAQ&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=perce-\nived%20by%20religious%20individuals%20as%20associated%20with%20the%20divine&f=f-\nalse] e-Study Guide for: Religion and Globalization by John L. Esposito, ISBN\n9780195176957\n - Cram101 Textbook Reviews, Jan 1, 2012 or 'sacred' (considered worthy of\n   spiritual respect or devotion; or inspiring awe or reverence among believers\n   in a given set of spiritual ideas). [http://books.google.com/books?id=3G-\n   GQI05TADsC&pg=PA169&lpg=PA169&dq=sacred,+the+state+of+being+holy&source=bl&o-\n   ts=P53SNT3RNq&sig=uoQqGDlu1O6QjJJ3VnLvldpR57o&hl=en&sa=X&ei=2S06UI_aBIz68QTC-\n   _YHoDA&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=sacred&f=false] Not Just Recovered But\n   Delivered II: He Is Able By Anthony Lightfoot - AuthorHouse, Sep 28, 2010 -\n   page 169 In other contexts, \"objects are often considered 'holy' or\n   'sacred' if used for spiritual purposes\", [http://books.google.com/books-\n   ?id=TumZdOG96NUC&pg=PT60&lpg=PT60&dq=objects+are+often+considered+'holy'+or+-\n   'sacred'+if+used+for+spiritual+purposes&source=bl&ots=6chLS8Vu7R&sig=O4m4GZJ-\n   Jo0ET6MdO8zgL0r-\n   1VJA&hl=en&sa=X&ei=LTE6UOzUFIf88gSWxYHwBQ&ved=0CEgQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=object-\n   s%20are%20often%20considered%20'holy'%20or%20'sacred'%20if%20used%20for%20sp-\n   iritual%20purposes&f=false] e-Study Guide for: The Worlds Religion by William\n   A Young, ISBN 9780205675111 - Cram101 Textbook Reviews, Jan 1, 2012 \n   such as the worship or service of gods. These terms can also be used in a non-\n   spiritual or semi-spiritual context (\"sacred truths\" in a constitution). [http://books.google.com/books?id=6zL6Icwcr7MC&pg=PT344&lpg=PT344&dq=sacred-\n   +truths%22+in+a+constitution&source=bl&ots=a5rqp7X4KE&sig=N1WNcXV-\n   9G6zqobD2BWkb5vLZew&hl=en&sa=X&ei=3jM6UPbyMYL28gSW74GIDw&ved=0CDsQ6AEwAg#v=o-\n   nepage&q=sacred%20truths%22%20in%20a%20constitution&f=false] e-Study Guide\n   for: Religion in America: An Historical Account of the Development of\n   American Religious Life by John Corrigan, ISBN 9780136158172 - Cram101\n   Textbook Reviews, Jan 1, 2012  It is often ascribed to people (\"a holy\n   man\" of religious occupation, \"holy prophet\" who is venerated by his\n   followers), objects (\"sacred artifact\" that is venerated and blessed ), -\n   [http://books.google.com/books?id=3GGQI05TADsC&pg=PA169&lpg=PA169&dq=sacred,-\n   +the+state+of+being+holy&source=bl&ots=P53SNT3RNq&sig=uoQqGDlu1O6QjJJ3VnLvld-\n   pR57o&hl=en&sa=X&ei=2S06UI_aBIz68QTC_YHoDA&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=sacre-\n   d&f=false] Not Just Recovered But Delivered II: He Is Able By Anthony\n   Lightfoot - AuthorHouse, Sep 28, 2010 - page 169 times (\"holy days\" of\n   spiritual introspection, such as during winter holidays), [http://books.-\n   google.com/books?id=3GGQI05TADsC&pg=PA169&lpg=PA169&dq=sacred,+the+state+of+-\n   being+holy&source=bl&ots=P53SNT3RNq&sig=uoQqGDlu1O6QjJJ3VnLvldpR57o&hl=en&sa-\n   =X&ei=2S06UI_aBIz68QTC_YHoDA&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=sacred&f=false] Not\n   Just Recovered But Delivered II: He Is Able By Anthony Lightfoot -\n   AuthorHouse, Sep 28, 2010 - page 169 or places (\"sacred ground\", \"holy\n   place\"). [http://books.google.com/books?id=3GGQI05TADsC&pg=PA169&lpg=PA1-\n   69&dq=sacred,+the+state+of+being+holy&source=bl&ots=P53SNT3RNq&sig=uoQqGDlu1-\n   O6QjJJ3VnLvldpR57o&hl=en&sa=X&ei=2S06UI_aBIz68QTC_YHoDA&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBA#v=on-\n   epage&q=sacred&f=false] Not Just Recovered But Delivered II: He Is Able By\n   Anthony Lightfoot - AuthorHouse, Sep 28, 2010 - page 169\n","linknr":364,"url":"Sacr